---
import ServiceIcon from "./ServiceIcon.astro";
---

<section id="services" class="bg-slate-800 py-16">
    <div class="py-8 px-4 mx-auto max-w-screen-xl sm:py-16 lg:px-6">
        <div class="max-w-screen-md mb-8 lg:mb-16">
            <h2 class="mb-4 text-4xl tracking-tight font-extrabold text-white">
                Services
            </h2>
            <p class="text-gray-400 sm:text-xl">
                Comprehensive DevSecOps solutions tailored to your
                infrastructure needs.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div
            class="space-y-8 md:grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 md:gap-12 md:space-y-0"
        >
            <!-- Service 1 -->
            <div>
                <div
                    class="flex justify-center items-center mb-4 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-blue-900 lg:h-12 lg:w-12"
                >
                    <ServiceIcon
                        icon="cloud-security"
                        class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-400 lg:w-6 lg:h-6"
                    />
                </div>
                <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold text-white">
                    Cloud Security
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-400">
                    Hardening cloud environments (AWS, Azure, GCP) ensuring
                    least privilege, IAM policies, and secure network
                    architectures.
                </p>
            </div>
            <!-- Service 2 -->
            <div>
                <div
                    class="flex justify-center items-center mb-4 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-blue-900 lg:h-12 lg:w-12"
                >
                    <!-- Icon for CI/CD -->
                    <ServiceIcon
                        icon="ci-cd"
                        class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-400 lg:w-6 lg:h-6"
                    />
                </div>
                <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold text-white">
                    CI/CD Hardening
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-400">
                    Implementing security gates in CI/CD pipelines (GitHub
                    Actions, GitLab CI, Jenkins). SAST/DAST integration.
                </p>
            </div>
            <!-- Service 3 -->
            <div>
                <div
                    class="flex justify-center items-center mb-4 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-blue-900 lg:h-12 lg:w-12"
                >
                    <ServiceIcon
                        icon="compliance"
                        class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-400 lg:w-6 lg:h-6"
                    />
                </div>
                <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold text-white">
                    Compliance & Governance
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-400">
                    Automating compliance checks for SOC2, HIPAA, and GDPR.
                    Infrastructure as Code (Terraform, Ansible) auditing.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="bg-slate-900 py-16">
    <div class="py-8 px-4 mx-auto max-w-screen-xl lg:py-16 lg:px-6">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-screen-md text-center mb-8 lg:mb-12">
            <h2 class="mb-4 text-4xl tracking-tight font-extrabold text-white">
                Strategic Engineering
            </h2>
            <p class="mb-5 font-light text-gray-400 sm:text-xl">
                High-impact initiatives for mature organizations.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-2">
            <!-- IDP -->
            <div class="p-6 bg-slate-800 rounded-lg border border-gray-700">
                <h3 class="mb-2 text-2xl font-bold text-white">
                    Platform Engineering & IDP
                </h3>
                <p class="font-light text-gray-400 mb-4">
                    Building secure, self-service platforms (Golden Paths) to
                    reduce cognitive load effectively.
                </p>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-400 space-y-2">
                    <li>
                        <strong>Golden Paths:</strong> Standardized templates for
                        services, CI/CD, and Terraform.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Secure-by-Default:</strong> Policy enforcement, secrets
                        management, and mtls baked in.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>DX Optimization:</strong> Improving deployment frequency
                        and reducing lead time.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <!-- FinOps + SRE -->
            <div class="p-6 bg-slate-800 rounded-lg border border-gray-700">
                <h3 class="mb-2 text-2xl font-bold text-white">
                    FinOps & SRE Audits
                </h3>
                <p class="font-light text-gray-400 mb-4">
                    Deep technical reviews to cut cloud spend without
                    compromising reliability.
                </p>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-400 space-y-2">
                    <li>
                        <strong>Cost Analysis:</strong> K8s rightsizing and detecting
                        architectural waste.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Reliability Gaps:</strong> SLO definition, error budget
                        policies, and DR readiness.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Actionable Roadmap:</strong> Prioritized list for
                        savings and risk reduction.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-1 mt-8">
            <!-- Sovereign AI -->
            <div class="p-6 bg-slate-800 rounded-lg border border-gray-700">
                <h3 class="mb-2 text-2xl font-bold text-white">
                    On-Prem & Sovereign AI
                </h3>
                <p class="font-light text-gray-400 mb-4">
                    Designing controllable, non-SaaS compute platforms for
                    critical workloads.
                </p>
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                    <div>
                        <h4 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">
                            Bare-Metal K8s
                        </h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">
                            High-performance clusters (Talos, Cozystack)
                            tailored for AI.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h4 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">
                            GPU Orchestration
                        </h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">
                            Efficient scheduling and isolation for
                            training/inference.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h4 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">
                            Data Sovereignty
                        </h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">
                            Strict compliance and locality for sensitive ML
                            pipelines.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
